      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEMI PEAKIN' (1) finished in the minors last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 400m at this track, taking a NG in a dynamic 22.76. Smart win two back and looks a key chance here. ZIPPING VIVID (5) goes very well here starting 16 times for six wins and four minors. Missed the frame latest (17.67) when fourth over 300m at Taree Super Track in a NG. Looks well placed here and among the chances. FLYING GODDESS (2) is first up since finishing fourth (30.88) in a Grade 4/5 at Taree Super Track over 525m ten weeks ago. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. MESSY AND UNTIDY (7) generally performs well over this distance.",
